BACKGROUND	O
OF	O
THE	O
INVENTION	O
1	O
.	O
Field	O
of	O
the	O
Invention	O
The	O
present	O
invention	O
relates	O
to	O
clocks	O
and	O
clock	O
radios	O
,	O
and	O
more	O
specifically	O
to	O
interactive	O
voice	O
controlled	O
clocks	O
and	O
clock	O
radios	O
.	O
The	O
methods	O
and	O
apparatus	O
of	O
the	O
invention	O
provide	O
for	O
setting	O
substantially	O
all	O
initial	O
parameters	O
for	O
a	O
clock	O
or	O
clock	O
radio	O
,	O
including	O
the	O
time	O
,	O
alarm	O
,	O
radio	O
