Art	O
Including	O
Information	O
Disclosed	O
Under	O
37	O
CFR	O
1	O
.	O
97	O
and	O
1	O
.	O
98	O
Over	O
the	O
years	O
the	O
modem	O
world	O
has	O
required	O
higher	O
and	O
higher	O
levels	O
of	O
interaction	O
and	O
interdependence	O
of	O
mankind	O
.	O
In	O
addition	O
,	O
people	O
seem	O
to	O
be	O
performing	O
many	O
more	O
of	O
their	O
activities	O
or	O
tasks	O
during	O
both	O
the	O
day	O
and	O
night	O
.	O
To	O
